article_title: As UnitedHealth Bails On Obamacare, Rivals Look To Expand

article_metadata.description: UnitedHealth Group is so far alone in its exit from several Obamacare exchanges. Centene, Anthem and other Blue Cross and Blue Shield plans are staying in the business of providing such coverage and looking at ways to expand.
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
